data.description: Is 3 your lucky number? This home boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a spacious 3-car garage, all ready for immediate occupancy! Recently repainted, it features brand new light fixtures throughout and LED vanity mirrors with adjustable lighting and anti-fog capabilities. Outside, you'll find fresh exterior paint, new sod in both the front and back yards, and a newly installed back fence. Professionally cleaned, the ground floor Main Bedroom is conveniently separated from the upstairs bedrooms and bonus room. Tucked away on a private gravel lane off Willow, this property offers privacy without any homeowner association restrictions (CCR's). Plus, it's conveniently close to stores, cinemas, restaurants, and more.
